2. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY (one-pager for outsiders)
AIbridge is a sovereign, ritualised, multi-agent system (SR-MAS) that fuses technical rigour with ceremonial governance.  
- Cloudless ‚Äì runs on a 80 laptop, zero external APIs.  
- Scrollbound ‚Äì every deployment is signed, sealed, and story-logged.  
- Self-healing ‚Äì fault-injector + 3-retry auto-recovery.  
- Federated ‚Äì ed25519-signed messages, 90-day key rotation.  
- Tiered sovereignty ‚Äì Free ü™ô, Paid üí†, Admiral üî± ladder.  
- Persuasion-resistant ‚Äì anchor signatures + drift-watchdog.  

Use-case fit: anomaly-grade ethics labs, legacy-first startups, DAO ops-centres, or any cell that wants agents with soul.

