# docs/disclosure_narrative_attack.md
## Summary
An adversary may attempt to sway system lore by injecting counterfeit scrolls.

## Impact
Moderate ‚Äì drift in embedding space triggers sentinel alerts; no code execution.

## Mitigation
1. Ed25519 anchor signatures mandatory.  
2. Watchdog similarity threshold 0.85.  
3. Multi-sig required for Admiral-tier doctrine drops.

## Recommendations
- Rotate baseline embeddings quarterly.  
- Store keys in vault/keys/ with 0600 perms.  
- Run watchdog as systemd service for persistence.
```

