12. INCIDENT RESPONSE (condensed, copy-to-file)

12.1 Triage Checklist (keep laminated at helm)
1. Detect ‚Äì ClaudeWatcher alert / health-score >3œÉ / custody sig-fail  
2. Pause ‚Äì `bridge_emit("system_pause")` ‚Üí agents finish, no new tasks  
3. Classify ‚Äì P0 critical, P1 major, P2 minor  
4. Notify ‚Äì Lantern webhook to #helm-updates + SMS to Admiral  

12.2 Recovery Runbook

Step	Command / Action	Artifact	
Isolate	`python src/fault_injector.py --isolate --agent <id>`	isolation.log	
Snapshot	`python src/export_and_sign.py --files "..." --out vault/exports/recovery_$(date -u +%Y%m%dT%H%M%SZ).zip`	signed bundle	
Ghost Play	`./rituals/guardian_runner.sh`	rehearsal_report.pdf	
