23. VERIFY THE SEAL (anyone, anywhere)

```bash
# 1. recompute hash
sha256sum AIbridge_Playbook_v1.18.zip
# 2. verify sig
python -c "from nacl.signing import VerifyKey;import json,base64,hashlib,sys;\
vk=VerifyKey(open('AIbridge_Playbook_v1.18.pub').read().strip(),encoder=HexEncoder);\
sig=base64.b64decode(open('AIbridge_Playbook_v1.18.zip.sig').read());\
vk.verify(hashlib.sha256(open('AIbridge_Playbook_v1.18.zip','rb').read()).digest(),sig);print('‚úÖ Scroll untampered.')"
```

