- FastAPI router `/bridge/sovereign/*`  
- Endpoints:  
  - `GET /policy`  
  - `POST /policy` (guarded)  
  - `GET /dominion-codex`  
  - `POST /dominion-codex` (guarded)  
- All calls pass through `check_route()`

---

3. Concordance Chain Manager (Node)
File: `scripts/chain_policy_manager.js`  
- Watch-mode: `fs.watch(.forge)` ‚Üí incremental harmonize  
- Snapshots drifted files to `.forge/.rollback/`  
- If Œº_concordance < 0.99 ‚Üí auto-rollback drifted targets  
- Appends history to `.forge/chain_history.jsonl`  
- Exit codes: 0 = aligned, 1 = guard rollback, 2 = fatal

---

