2.3 Genesis Bus ‚Äì Pub-Sub Spine

```python
# bridge_core/lattice/genesis_bus.py
class GenesisBus:
    def publish(self, topic: str, payload: Any):
        for handler in self._subs.get(topic, []):
            handler(payload)
```

