üßµ Thread 17 ‚Äì Exile-Path CLI

File: `brh/bin/brh-exile` (self-contained, POSIX-sh)

```sh
#!/system/bin/sh   # Termux + alpine + busybox
# brh-exile --start  --> spawn isolated BRH shard
set -e
BRH_ROOT="${BRH_ROOT:-/data/brh}"
EXILE_SHARD="$BRH_ROOT/exile/$$"
mkdir -p "$EXILE_SHARD"/{db,tmp,cfg}
cat > "$EXILE_SHARD/cfg/env.toml" <<EOF
[quiet_corner]
enable = true
isolation_level = "exile"
hum_threshold = 0.95
glow_color = "#6EE7B7"
EOF
echo "üåë Exile shard ready at $EXILE_SHARD"
export BRH_CFG="$EXILE_SHARD/cfg/env.toml"
export BRH_DB="$EXILE_SHARD/db/ledger.db"
exec brh-runtime "$@"
```

Install:

```
chmod +x brh/bin/brh-exile
sudo mv brh/bin/brh-exile /usr/local/bin/
brh-exile --start  # drops you into isolated runtime
```

