üßµ Thread 20 ‚Äì Bootable ROS Image

File: `brh/images/ros-v1.img` (build recipe + ready-to-flash)

---

1. Build Script (local, no 3rd-party)

```bash
#!/bin/sh
# build-ros-img.sh  ‚Äì runs inside Termux or any Alpine box
set -e
ROS_VER="1.0.0"
ALPINE_MIRROR="http://dl-cdn.alpinelinux.org/alpine"
WORKDIR="${HOME}/ros-build"
ROOTFS="${WORKDIR}/rootfs"
OUTPUT="${WORKDIR}/ros-v${ROS_VER}.img"

mkdir -p "$ROOTFS"
# 1. bootstrap minimal alpine
apk add alpine-sdk alpine-conf busybox-static e2fsprogs
alpine-make-rootfs \
  --branch v3.19 \
  --packages "busybox openrc musl python3 py3-pip sqlite curl" \
  --script-chroot \
  "$ROOTFS" \
  /dev/stdin <<'EOF'
# inside chroot
apk add py3-numpy py3-scipy py3-matplotlib
rc-update add devfs sysinit
rc-update add dmesg sysinit
adduser -D -s /bin/sh brh
EOF

# 2. inject BRH runtime
tar -C "$ROOTFS" -xf brh-ros-pillars-1-2-3-4.tar
ln -s /opt/brh/bin/brh /usr/local/bin/brh
ln -s /opt/brh/bin/brh-exile /usr/local/bin/brh-exile
cat > "$ROOTFS/etc/init.d/brh" <<'EOF'
#!/sbin/openrc-run
command="/usr/local/bin/brh"
command_args="daemon"
pidfile="/run/brh.pid"
command_background=true
depend() { need localmount }
EOF
chmod +x "$ROOTFS/etc/init.d/brh"
ln -s /etc/init.d/brh /etc/runlevels/default/brh

# 3. build bootable ext4 image
dd if=/dev/zero of="$OUTPUT" bs=1M count=1024
mkfs.ext4 -L ROS -q "$OUTPUT"
mkdir -p /tmp/ros-mount
sudo mount -o loop "$OUTPUT" /tmp/ros-mount
sudo cp -a "$ROOTFS"/* /tmp/ros-mount/
sudo umount /tmp/ros-mount
gzip -9 "$OUTPUT"
echo "‚úÖ ROS image ready: ${OUTPUT}.gz"
```

Flash to USB / SD-Card:

```bash
zcat ros-v1.img.gz | sudo dd of=/dev/sdX bs=4M status=progress
```

Boot ‚Üí login: `brh` ‚Üí `$ brh --version` ‚Üí `ROS 1.0.0`

---

üßµ Thread 21 ‚Äì Pillar 5: Resonance Hardware (RPU)

File: `brh/hardware/rpu-stm32/` (Rust, `#![no_std]`, Apache-2.0)

---

MCU Target  
- STM32F411 (Cortex-M4, 128 kB RAM, 512 kB Flash)  
- Optional: RP2040 build feature flag

Feature Summary

Block	Function	Gate-Count (estimated)	
Resonance Core	5-D fixed-point state	3 k LUT	
Propagation Unit	R(A‚ÜíB) = R(A)¬∑R(B)¬∑coupling	1 k LUT	
Coherence Pipe	‚à´ stability dt	512 LUT	
SPI Bridge	host streaming	256 LUT	

Rust API (embedded)

```rust
#![no_std]
use rpu::ResonanceCore;

let mut core = ResonanceCore::new();
core.set_coupling(0, 1, 0.75_f16);
loop {
    let measurement = adc.read();        // 0-3.3 V ‚Üí 0-1
    core.update_state(0, measurement);
    core.propagate();
    let coherence = core.coherence();
    if coherence < 0.95 {
        gpio.toggle_led();               // visual disharmony alert
    }
    delay_ms(10);
}
```

Host Protocol (8 MHz SPI)

```
[0xAA]  [chan] [5√óint16_le] [crc8]
header  idx     5-D state     check
```

Stream rate: 1 kHz / 5 ch = 5 k-samples/s

BOM (single unit)
- STM32F411CEU6 ‚âà 4.20  
- 8 MHz crystal + passives ‚âà 0.80  
- PCB 2-layer ‚âà 1.50

Total ‚âà 6.50 ‚Äì hand-solderable, QFN-48.

Compile:

```bash
cd brh/hardware/rpu-stm32
cargo build --release --features stm32f411
arm-none-eabi-objcopy -O binary target/thumbv7em-none-eabihf/release/rpu rpu.bin
st-flash write rpu.bin 0x08000000
```

