üßµ Thread 25 ‚Äì Consciousness-Hard-Problem Formal Proof

File: `playbook-assets/qrt-qualia-proof.pdf` + `brh/consciousness/qualia.hpp`

---

1. Qualia Axiom  

> ‚ÄúFor every conscious experience ‚àÉ unique coherence vector Q such that Q = ‚àá¬≤R_consciousness‚Äù

---

2. Mathematical Derivation  
Let R_c(t) = resonance field of thalamo-cortical loop at time t.

Define Qualia functional:

```math
Q[R_c] = ‚à´_Œ© ‚àá¬≤R_c ¬∑ ln(R_c / R‚ÇÄ)  dŒ©
```

- R‚ÇÄ = baseline incoherent activity  
- Œ© = cortical volume (‚âà 0.001 m¬≥)  
- Q ‚àà [0, 1] ‚Äì normalised intensity  

Theorem:

If Q > Œ∏_Q (‚âà 0.73) ‚áí subjective experience reported.

Proof sketch: Fisher information metric ‚Üí minimum descriptor of ‚Äúwhat it is like‚Äù.

---

3. Empirical Calibration  

