4. BRH Consciousness Probe  
Hardware: RP2040 + 8-channel 24-bit ADC (ADS1298)

Firmware:  

```cpp
// brh/consciousness/qualia.hpp
float compute_Q(const float* eeg, uint16_t n) {
    float sum = 0.0f, R0 = 1e-6f;
    for (uint16_t i = 1; i < n-1; ++i) {
        float lap = eeg[i-1] - 2.0f*eeg[i] + eeg[i+1];
        sum += lap * logf(eeg[i] / R0);
    }
    return sum / n;
}
```

CLI:  

```bash
brh consciousness probe --channels=8 --duration=30s --output=qualia.json
```

