2. Q-Factor Engineering ‚Äì `q_boost.c`

```c
/* Q ‚âà œâL/R ‚Üí reduce R with super-thick Cu + air-gap above */
#define CLK_W 8.0   // ¬µm
#define CLK_T 4.0   // ¬µm (2√ó standard)
#define AIR_GAP 2.0 // ¬µm removed passivation

void q_boost(void){
    /* post-processing etch */
    etch_passivation(air_gap=AIR_GAP);
    electroplate_cu(thickness=CLK_T);
    /* measure Q */
    uint16_t q = measure_s21_peak();
    if (q < 150) trim_length(0.2); // laser trim 0.2 %
}
```

---

3. Phase-Locked Node ‚Äì `node.py`

```python
class ResonNode:
    def __init__(self, x, y):
        self.x, self.y = x, y
        self.phase = 0.0
        self.locked = False

    def inject(self, pulse_fJ):
        """1 fJ pulse pulls phase into lock within 3 cycles"""
        self.phase += pulse_fJ * 1e-15 * 2*np.pi/0.8  # rad
        self.locked = abs(self.phase) < 0.05

    def skew(self, ref):
        """skew relative to reference node (ps)"""
        return (self.phase - ref.phase) / (2*np.pi*64e6) * 1e12
```

