2. Œ∏ Phase Extractor ‚Äì `theta_phase.c`

```c
#include "theta_dsp.h"

#define THETA_LO 4.0f
#define THETA_HI 12.0f

float theta_phase = 0;

void theta_track(float x){
    static float x_old = 0, y_old = 0;
    /* 2nd-order IIR 8 Hz resonator */
    float y = 1.88f*y_old - 0.92f*x_old + 0.04f*x;
    x_old = x; y_old = y;
    theta_phase = atan2f(y, x);
}
```

