4. Ripple Detector ‚Äì `ripple_detect.py`

```python
def detect_ripple(eeg, fs=2000):
    from scipy.signal import butter, sosfilt
    sos = butter(4, [110, 250], btype='band', fs=fs, output='sos')
    rip = sosfilt(sos, eeg)
    envelope = np.abs(hilbert(rip))
    return envelope > 6*np.std(envelope)  # bool array
```

