5. Replay Trigger ‚Äì `replay_seq.c`

```c
uint16_t seq[16] = {3,7,5,12,8,2,14,6,11,1,15,4,9,0,13,10};

void replay_if_ripple(void){
    if (detect_ripple()){
        for (uint8_t i=0;i<16;i++){
            uint8_t ch = seq[i];
            float delay = i * 125; // 8 Hz ‚Üí 125 ms
            schedule_stim(ch, delay);
        }
    }
}
```

