5. 60 GHz Rectenna ‚Äì `rectenna.py`

```python
# diode-connected NMOS 40 nm, 28 % PCE
def rectenna_pce(pin_dbm):
    return 0.28 if pin_dbm > -15 else 0.15

def harvested_power(density_dbm_cm2, area_cm2):
    pin = density_dbm_cm2 + 10*np.log10(area_cm2)
    return 1e3 * rectenna_pce(pin) * 10**((pin-30)/10)  # mW

print(harvested_power(-5, 4))  # 8 mW
```

