3. EHG Extraction ‚Äì `ehg.c`

```c
#define EHG_LO 0.003f  // Hz
#define EHG_HI 0.3f    // Hz

float ehg_power(void){
    float sum = 0;
    for (uint8_t ch=0; ch<16; ch++){
        float x = iir_bandpass(afe_read(ch), EHG_LO, EHG_HI, 4.0);
        sum += x*x;
    }
    return sum / 16.0f;
}
```

