6. Energy Harvest ‚Äì `abdominal_piezo.py`

```python
def piezo_power(g=1.0, f=1.0):  # g in m/s¬≤, f in Hz
    m_eff = 2e-3  # kg
    zeta = 0.04
    w_n = 2*np.pi*1  # rad/s
    a = g / w_n**2
    p = 0.5 * m_eff * (a*w_n)**2 * 2*zeta / w_n
    return p * 1e3  # mW

print(piezo_power(1, 1))  # 1.6 mW
```

