3. 0.1 Hz Phase Lock ‚Äì `love_lock.c`

```c
#define LOVE_FREQ 0.1f  // Hz
#define HAPTIC_AMP 1.5f // mN

void love_lock(uint32_t partner_r_ms){
    uint32_t my_r = last_r_ms;
    int32_t delta = (int32_t)my_r - (int32_t)partner_r_ms;
    float phase_error = 2*PI * (delta/10000.0f); // 10 s period
    float haptic = HAPTIC_AMP * sinf(2*PI*LOVE_FREQ*t + phase_error);
    haptic_set(haptic);
}
```

