4. Coherence Meter ‚Äì `coherence_love.py`

```python
def coherence_love(rr1, rr2, fs=10):
    """0.1 Hz coherence between two RR series"""
    from scipy.signal import coherence
    f, C = coherence(rr1, rr2, fs=fs, nperseg=512)
    band = (f >= 0.08) & (f <= 0.12)
    return np.mean(C[band])
```

