3. Pendulum Driver ‚Äì `escapement.c`

```c
#define L 13.5f      // m (length)
#define G 9.80665f
#define T_NAT (2*PI*sqrtf(L/G))  // 7.37 s

void escapement_tick(void){
    /* electromagnetic kick every 7.37 s to maintain 0.001 Hz beat */
    static uint32_t tick = 0;
    if (tick % 7370 == 0){ // 7370 √ó 1 ms = 7.37 s
        coil_pulse(50);    // 50 ms, 0.5 N
    }
    tick++;
}
```

