4. 1/f Noise Corner ‚Äì `flicker_entropy.py`

```python
def flicker_corner(vdc, t):
    """return frequency where 1/f noise = thermal noise"""
    k = 1.38e-23
    T = 300
    gm = 1e-6  # S
    Cox = 5e-15  # F
    Kf = 2e-28  # process param
    Sthermal = 4*k*T*gm
    Sflicker = Kf * gm**2 / (Cox * vdc**2 * 1)
    return Sthermal / Sflicker  # ~ 3 ¬µHz for 1 V
```

---

5. Leakage Timer ‚Äì `leakage_clock.c`

```c
/* uses gate leakage to drift floating gate ~1 mV/yr */
#define DRIFT_RATE 3.2e-12  // V/s

float time_since_heat_death(void){
    float drift = read_fgate_drift();
    return drift / DRIFT_RATE; // seconds
}
```

