- On-chip SFQ (Single-Flux-Quantum) circuits store one flux quantum Œ¶‚ÇÄ = h/(2e) = 2.067 834 mV¬∑ps ‚Äì the smallest possible pulse in Nature.  
- Energy: zero static power; impulse pump via 1550 nm femto-laser at 1 pJ per toggle ‚Üí 1 ¬µW at 1 MHz rep-rate.  
