5. Fourier Duality Check ‚Äì `duality_test.py`

```python
def duality_test(v_t):
    """V(t) = Œ¶‚ÇÄ¬∑Œ¥(t)  ‚Üî  V(f) = Œ¶‚ÇÄ (constant)"""
    from numpy.fft import fft
    V_f = fft(v_t)
    return np.allclose(V_f, 2.067834e-3)  # flat spectrum
```

