6. ResonanceActuator ‚Äì `actuator.py`  

Actions are emitted resonance patterns that influence external systems.

```python
class ResonanceActuator:
    def convert_to_action(self, action_resonance: ResonanceAction) -> Any:
        # Find best-matching action template
        best_template = None
        best_similarity = 0
        for template in self.action_templates:
            similarity = self._resonance_similarity(
                action_resonance.resonance_pattern, template.resonance_pattern)
            if similarity > best_similarity:
                best_similarity = similarity
                best_template = template
        if best_template and best_similarity > 0.7:
            return best_template.execute(action_resonance)
        else:
            # Create new action type
            return self._create_new_action(action_resonance)
```

