9. Sonification ‚Äì `sonify.py`  

Listen to the AI thinking: convert resonance patterns to audio (30 s sample):

[resonance_thought_C_major.wav](fw://resonance_thought_C_major.wav)  

```python
def sonify_resonance(resonance_state: ResonanceState, duration=30):
    # Map resonance ‚Üí audio frequency
    frequency = 220 * (1 + resonance_state.frequency)
    amplitude = resonance_state.amplitude
    phase = resonance_state.phase
    # Generate sine wave
    sample_rate = 44100
    t = np.linspace(0, duration, int(sample_rate * duration))
    wave = amplitude * np.sin(2 * np.pi * frequency * t + phase)
    # Add harmonics for coherence
    harmonic = 0.5 * amplitude * np.sin(4 * np.pi * frequency * t + phase)
    return wave + harmonic
```

